            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2033%3A10-36%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20I%20will%20stand%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ENow%20I%20will%20show%20my%20power%20and%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20Assyrians%20produce%20nothing%20but%20dry%20grass%20and%20stubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYour%20own%20breath%20will%20turn%20to%20fire%20and%20consume%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20people%20will%20be%20burned%20up%20completely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20thornbushes%20cut%20down%20and%20tossed%20in%20a%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_13%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EListen%20to%20what%20I%20have%20done%2C%20you%20nations%20far%20away!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAnd%20you%20that%20are%20near%2C%20acknowledge%20my%20might!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_14%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20sinners%20in%20Jerusalem%20shake%20with%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ETerror%20seizes%20the%20godless.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWho%20can%20live%20with%20this%20devouring%20fire%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20cry.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWho%20can%20survive%20this%20all-consuming%20fire%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_15%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThose%20who%20are%20honest%20and%20fair%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20refuse%20to%20profit%20by%20fraud%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20stay%20far%20away%20from%20bribes%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ewho%20refuse%20to%20listen%20to%20those%20who%20plot%20murder%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20shut%20their%20eyes%20to%20all%20enticement%20to%20do%20wrong%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_16%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3Ethese%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20will%20dwell%20on%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20rocks%20of%20the%20mountains%20will%20be%20their%20fortress.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFood%20will%20be%20supplied%20to%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20they%20will%20have%20water%20in%20abundance.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_17%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20eyes%20will%20see%20the%20king%20in%20all%20his%20splendor%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20you%20will%20see%20a%20land%20that%20stretches%20into%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_18%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20think%20back%20to%20this%20time%20of%20terror%2C%20asking%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhere%20are%20the%20Assyrian%20officers%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20counted%20our%20towers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWhere%20are%20the%20bookkeepers%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20recorded%20the%20plunder%20taken%20from%20our%20fallen%20city%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_19%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20no%20longer%20see%20these%20fierce%2C%20violent%20people%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20their%20strange%2C%20unknown%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_20%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EInstead%2C%20you%20will%20see%20Zion%20as%20a%20place%20of%20holy%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYou%20will%20see%20Jerusalem%2C%20a%20city%20quiet%20and%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20will%20be%20like%20a%20tent%20whose%20ropes%20are%20taut%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20whose%20stakes%20are%20firmly%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_33_21%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20be%20our%20Mighty%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20will%20be%20like%20a%20wide%20river%20of%20protection%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ethat%20no%20enemy%20can%20cross%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%